      "slide_length": 5
    },
    {
      "slide_title": "",
      "slide_text": "Before I went under the knife, I wondered if the Mayans were going to end up being right.",
      "bg_color": "white",
      "bg_image": "",
      "text_color": "black",
      "text_font": "Times New Roman",
      "text_size": "500%",
      "text_align": "center",
      "audio_file": "",
      "video_file": "",
      "slide_length": 5
    },
    {
      "slide_title": "",
      "slide_text": "I would position my arms above my head, close my eyes, and count down from 10.<br><br>I wouldn't make it to 6.",
      "bg_color": "white",
      "bg_image": "",
      "text_color": "black",
      "text_font": "Times New Roman",
      "text_size": "500%",
      "text_align": "center",
      "audio_file": "",
      "video_file": "",
      "slide_length": 5
    },
    {
      "slide_title": "",
      "slide_text": "A dense throbbing would wake me. My knee would feel like a drained volcano, caved out and ready to burst.",
      "bg_color": "white",
      "bg_image": "",
      "text_color": "black",
      "text_font": "Times New Roman",
      "text_size": "500%",
      "text_align": "center",
      "audio_file": "",
      "video_file": "",
      "slide_length": 5
    },
    {
      "slide_title": "",
      "slide_text": "A blue, machine-operated sling should be holding and stretching my leg for me. My throat would be dry and the lights in the recovery room dim.",
      "bg_color": "white",
      "bg_image": "",
      "text_color": "black",
      "text_font": "Times New Roman",
      "text_size": "500%",
      "text_align": "center",
      "audio_file": "",
      "video_file": "",
      "slide_length": 5
    },
    {
      "slide_title": "",
      "slide_text": "It would take me awhile to realize I was alone, even longer to call out to someone.<br><br>I would try to dismiss the fear, but it would linger like smudges on a chalkboard.",
      "bg_color": "white",
      "bg_image": "",
      "text_color": "black",
      "text_font": "Times New Roman",
      "text_size": "500%",
      "text_align": "center",
      "audio_file": "",
      "video_file": "",
      "slide_length": 5
    },
    {
      "slide_title": "",
      "slide_text": "I would need a wheelchair, or at least a couple crutches. I couldn\u2019t afford to tear the fresh stitches in my knee. Caution would be crucial.",
      "bg_color": "white",
      "bg_image": "",
      "text_color": "black",
      "text_font": "Times New Roman",
      "text_size": "500%",
      "text_align": "center",
      "audio_file": "",
      "video_file": "",
      "slide_length": 5
    },
    {
      "slide_title": "",
      "slide_text": "Before I went under the knife, I wondered if the Mayans were going to end up being right.",
      "bg_color": "white",
      "bg_image": "",
      "text_color": "black",
      "text_font": "Times New Roman",
      "text_size": "500%",
      "text_align": "center",
      "audio_file": "",
      "video_file": "",
      "slide_length": 5
    },
    {
      "slide_title": "",
      "slide_text": "But eventually, I\u2019m sure I\u2019d grow scared. I could only think about my knee for so long. Eventually I would wonder about the outside world, but I\u2019d be too afraid to look out the window.",
      "bg_color": "white",
      "bg_image": "",
      "text_color": "black",
      "text_font": "Times New Roman",
      "text_size": "500%",
      "text_align": "center",
      "audio_file": "",
      "video_file": "",
      "slide_length": 5
    },
    {
      "slide_title": "",
      "slide_text": "I\u2019d wonder why this is happening to me, whether it was just bad luck or something else.",
      "bg_color": "white",
      "bg_image": "",
      "text_color": "black",
      "text_font": "Times New Roman",
      "text_size": "500%",
      "text_align": "center",
      "audio_file": "",
      "video_file": "",
      "slide_length": 5
    },
    {
      "slide_title": "",
      "slide_text": "Why me, an ex-Catholic with bad knees and a destructive love for basketball?<br><br>Was this a punishment for my lack of faith? Or was I chosen to overcome a great test?",
      "bg_color": "white",
      "bg_image": "",
      "text_color": "black",
      "text_font": "Times New Roman",
      "text_size": "500%",
      "text_align": "center",
      "audio_file": "",
      "video_file": "",
      "slide_length": 5
    },
    {
      "slide_title": "",
      "slide_text": "I saw myself on a basketball court in a spaceship. I would have to play a game against intergalactic all-stars. I had to win, or else everyone lost.<br><br>Big, big stakes.",
      "bg_color": "white",
      "bg_image": "",
      "text_color": "black",
      "text_font": "Times New Roman",
      "text_size": "500%",
      "text_align": "center",
      "audio_file": "",
      "video_file": "",
      "slide_length": 5
    },
    {
      "slide_title": "",
      "slide_text": "I\u2019d box out, dive for loose balls, nail open jump shots.<br>I\u2019d forget I even had surgery last winter.<br> I\u2019d prove to everyone my knees weren\u2019t that bad after all, that I could play with the best of them.",
      "bg_color": "white",
      "bg_image": "",
      "text_color": "black",
      "text_font": "Times New Roman",
      "text_size": "500%",
      "text_align": "center",
      "audio_file": "",
      "video_file": "",
      "slide_length": 5
    },
    {
      "slide_title": "",
      "slide_text": "In the final seconds, I leap high into the air from half court\u2026",
      "bg_color": "white",
      "bg_image": "",
      "text_color": "black",
      "text_font": "Times New Roman",
      "text_size": "500%",
      "text_align": "center",
      "audio_file": "",
      "video_file": "",
      "slide_length": 5
    },
    {
      "slide_title": "",
      "slide_text": "Three\u2014<br><br><br>I soar over all the all-stars, all jealous of my outstanding range of motion and flexibility\u2026",
      "bg_color": "white",
      "bg_image": "",
      "text_color": "black",
      "text_font": "Times New Roman",
      "text_size": "300%",
      "text_align": "center",
      "audio_file": "",
      "video_file": "",
      "slide_length": 5
    },
    {
      "slide_title": "",
      "slide_text": "Two\u2014<br><br><br>The center sets his feet and jumps, arms extending straight up to deny me\u2026",
      "bg_color": "white",
      "bg_image": "",
      "text_color": "black",
      "text_font": "Times New Roman",
      "text_size": "300%",
      "text_align": "center",
      "audio_file": "",
      "video_file": "",
      "slide_length": 5
    },
    {
      "slide_title": "",
      "slide_text": "One\u2014<br><br><br>I slam dunk that shit and save Earth, but when I land, both knees simultaneously shatter.",
      "bg_color": "white",
      "bg_image": "",
      "text_color": "black",
      "text_font": "Times New Roman",
      "text_size": "500%",
      "text_align": "center",
      "audio_file": "",
      "video_file": "",
      "slide_length": 5
    },
    {
      "slide_title": "",
      "slide_text": "When I first feel pain, right when my knees both buckle and I fall to the floor, it\u2019ll sink in, really for the first time, that the Mayans were fucking right.",
      "bg_color": "white",
      "bg_image": "",
      "text_color": "black",
      "text_font": "Times New Roman",
      "text_size": "500%",
      "text_align": "center",
      "audio_file": "",
      "video_file": "",
      "slide_length": 5
    }
  ]
}